"""
Desktop GUI scaffold for configuring and previewing SCEPTer scenarios.

This module currently provides a desktop workflow for:

1. editing synthetic multi-belt constellation definitions
2. editing an optional RAS-station geometry
3. editing persistent antenna/frequency settings
4. running a persistent grid/contour-spacing analyzer
5. previewing Earth, satellites, and optional selected-satellite contours in a
   3D viewer
6. running the GPU direct-EPFD workflow from the configured GUI state
"""

